{"tid":1658821,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"真義士。荊軻","createTime":"2019-10-16T15:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T02:27:20.000Z","uid":314927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b15914bbca078a325df931daf2f4e4f3c563354d","tid":1658821,"uid":314927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"荊軻乃真義士，單人匹馬對付秦王政，圖窮匕現。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，人地下下向我們頭目、主力、高曝光率人物落手，製造恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n我地就日日係度撚狗，拆地鐵，無關痛癢。佢驚你條柒咩。<br />\n<br />\n有人提議圍林奠就即刻比人屌。<br />\n<br />\n我明我地唔應該送頭，但我們需要真義士。像荊軻一樣既義士。"},{"pid":"3b3edf3d1b3451c80991456ba444417f6837d653","tid":1658821,"uid":314927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:43:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fb4e563b8d28c9935be2fea32625949ae897e80","tid":1658821,"uid":314927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b26f85405771112e307e45df62517b7b210f1a1d","tid":1658821,"uid":314927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1b3f69ae88875338e88090be64a06f7b705812c2","tid":1658821,"uid":314927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}